    "Compared to MLH and MLHT, there's a minor improvement in stock profitability.",
    "However, the performance of ETH cryptocurrency dropped by over 20% due to the introduction of rule-based methods as auxiliary agents, which are specialized only for stocks.",
    "Effectiveness of Augmented Tools (RQ3)As previously discussed, while the addition of auxiliary agents to stock investments results in profit improvements, it causes a considerable performance decline in cryptocurrencies.",
    "Thus, we conduct the experiment that decisions are made solely by augmented tools, such as rule-based methods serving as auxiliary agents.",
    "We conducted the experiment in which various auxiliary agents provided both decisions and their explanations."
